| * ZapMan - David O'Shea *
| *************************

mode_man
Unix manpage mode by David O'Shea.
For more details there is a help file available.

MAN_SEARCH <string>
Search for a manpage (uses Man$Path).
The parameter can be either "command" or "command(section)"
eg. "Mail" or "Mail(1)"

MAN_REGULAR
Convert the selection to regular font.

MAN_BOLD
Convert the selection to bold font.
This only works on regular text.

MAN_UNDERLINE
Convert the selection to underlined font.
This only works on regular text.
